ces may also have diffused benefits that{\textbackslash}ncan extend to their families and communities. It would be advantageous{\textbackslash}nfor correctional authorities and policy makers to consider the{\textbackslash}npotentially pivotal role of long termers and lifers in efforts to{\textbackslash}nmitigate the negative consequences of incarceration.},
